a concise and beatiful rendition about the history of india this is a thoughtful and well researched book . it answers some of the questions which bother most indians are we aryans or dravidians , how did the indus valley civilization dissappear . the manner in which they explain the myths like the one about the vijayanagar empire tells us about the research put in by the authors . i would recommend this book to novices as well as connosieurs of indian histor